{"data":[{"date":"07:25 23/08","title":"N\u00d3NG: Tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfu tr\u00ean VTV6","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/nong-tran-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-se-duoc-chieu-tren-vtv6.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd t\u1eeb VOV, \u0111\u00e0i truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh Vi\u1ec7t Nam VTV s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp s\u00f3ng nguy\u00ean tr\u1ea1ng c\u00e1c m\u00f4n thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, trong \u0111\u00f3 bao g\u1ed3m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay 23/8.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<h2>Tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfu tr\u00ean VTV6<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"N\u00d3NG Tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfu tr\u00ean h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"N\u00d3NG Tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfu tr\u00ean h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/NONG-Tran-Olympic-Viet-Nam-vs-Olympic-Bahrain-se-duoc-chieu-tren-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>NHM s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam\u00a0vs Olympic Bahrain tr\u00ean VTV6</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e0i ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i Vi\u1ec7t Nam VOV c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng ASIAD 2018, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 th\u1ec3 thao n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u00e1c m\u00f4n thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam m\u00e0 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0o t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng 1/8.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 theo d\u00f5i thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n h\u01a1n ASIAD, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y VTV \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng v\u0103n xin ti\u1ebfp s\u00f3ng nguy\u00ean tr\u1ea1ng ASIAD v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd t\u1eeb ph\u00eda VOV. Hai b\u00ean \u0111ang tri\u1ec3n khai k\u00fd th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebfp s\u00f3ng c\u00e1c ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u0169ng ghi r\u00f5 vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebfp s\u00f3ng, tr\u00edch d\u1eabn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ghi r\u00f5 ngu\u1ed3n, gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean tr\u1ea1ng logo VOV b\u1edfi c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ph\u00e1p l\u00fd trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i. Nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc ti\u1ebfp s\u00f3ng nguy\u00ean tr\u1ea1ng ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u00e0i ti\u1ebfp s\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00e8n c\u00e1c ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh kh\u00e1c, kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u1eaft qu\u00e3ng trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ti\u1ebfp s\u00f3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">VTV s\u1ebd th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng. Kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem tr\u00ean ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh ASIAD tr\u00ean k\u00eanh VTV6. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tin kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 vui h\u01a1n v\u1edbi NHM n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u2018xem l\u1eadu\u2019 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf ASIAD.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-19h30-ngay-238-viet-tiep-ky-tich-168-195103.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-19h30-ngay-238-viet-tiep-ky-tich.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-19h30-ngay-238-viet-tiep-ky-tich-168-195103.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain (19h30 ng\u00e0y 23/8): Vi\u1ebft ti\u1ebfp k\u1ef3 t\u00edch</span><br>\r\n19h30 t\u1ed1i nay, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra. V\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/viet-nam-duoc-khen-co-lua-cau-thu-tre-tot-hon-thai-lan-168-195100.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/viet-nam-duoc-khen-co-lua-cau-thu-tre-tot-hon-thai-lan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/viet-nam-duoc-khen-co-lua-cau-thu-tre-tot-hon-thai-lan-168-195100.html\">Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khen c\u00f3 l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n Th\u00e1i Lan</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u00e0 gi\u1edd l\u00e0 t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, c\u00e2y b\u00fat c\u1ee7a t\u1edd Fox Sports Asia \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truong-doan-bahrain-chi-ra-3-ngoi-sao-nguy-hiem-nhat-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-195099.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/truong-doan-bahrain-chi-ra-3-ngoi-sao-nguy-hiem-nhat-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truong-doan-bahrain-chi-ra-3-ngoi-sao-nguy-hiem-nhat-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-195099.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n Bahrain ch\u1ec9 ra 3 ng\u00f4i sao nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nTrao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n \u0110T Olympic Bahrain t\u1ecf ra \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t c\u00f3 trong tay HLV Park Hang Seo.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-don-hung-tin-ve-nhan-su-truoc-tran-gap-bahrain-168-195101.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/olympic-viet-nam-don-hung-tin-ve-nhan-su-truoc-tran-gap-bahrain.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-don-hung-tin-ve-nhan-su-truoc-tran-gap-bahrain-168-195101.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00f3n hung tin v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Bahrain</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Bahrain t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng knock-out v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t tin kh\u00f4ng vui v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%;font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2675","checkdouble":"195106"},{"date":"08:12 23/08","title":"HLV Barcelona ho\u00e0i nghi v\u1ec1 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/18/ernesto-valverde-phat-bieu-ve-cong-nghe-var.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ernesto Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR. HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Barcelona c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ho\u00e0i nghi v\u1ec1 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a n\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1.</h2><br>\r\n<h2>VAR ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn kh\u1eafp th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua, VAR (c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd video) ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn tr\u00ean to\u00e0n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. B\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, n\u00f3 d\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn, \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 World Cup 2018 v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, VAR c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0a chu\u1ed9ng. La Liga m\u00f9a m\u1edbi 2018/19 c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm s\u1ef1 c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng cho nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi tham gia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ernesto Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ernesto Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/30/Ernesto-Valverde-phat-bieu-ve-cong-nghe-VAR-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ho\u00e0i nghi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>Valverde nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t</h2>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt l\u00e0 VAR v\u1eabn \u0111ang g\u00e2y ra s\u1ef1 tranh c\u00e3i \u1edf nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng. V\u00e0 HLV Ernesto Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00e2u d\u00e0i c\u1ee7a n\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;C\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c l\u00e0 c\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd video \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u00edch nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 c\u00f4ng t\u00e2m \u1edf c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m&rdquo;, \u00f4ng n\u00f3i tr\u00ean trang web ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Barca. &ldquo;Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft n\u00f3 c\u00f3 mang l\u1ea1i t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng ph\u1ee5 hay kh\u00f4ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n VAR l\u00e0m gi\u00e1n \u0111o\u1ea1n t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. \u0110i\u1ec1u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e0 n\u00f3 di\u1ec5n ra r\u1ea5t nhanh, \u00edt khi b\u1ecb gi\u00e1n \u0111o\u1ea1n. C\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean g\u00e2y \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng cho t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;&ldquo;T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng tranh c\u00e3i h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1edbi t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng xung quanh v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba. Nh\u01b0ng \u1edf chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee3p l\u1ec7 v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. T\u00f4i \u0111ang ch\u1edd c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR t\u1ea1i La Liga s\u1ebd ra sao.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i La Liga 2018/19, Barca \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u su\u00f4n s\u1ebb sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Deportivo Alaves ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Camp Nou.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Barcelona tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/ivan-rakitic-bat-ngo-ra-yeu-sach-voi-barca-180-195091.html\">Ivan Rakitic b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd ra y\u00eau s\u00e1ch v\u1edbi Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/sao-tre-barca-lap-hattrick-vao-luoi-real-madrid-328-195081.html\">Sao tr\u1ebb Barca l\u1eadp hattrick v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ac-milan-muon-mua-adrien-rabiot-176-195061.html\">L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n \u00f4ng l\u1edbn c\u1ea1nh tranh Rabiot c\u00f9ng Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/ac-milan-gia-nhap-cuoc-dua-gianh-rabiot-voi-barca-180-195051.html\">AC Milan gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh sao PSG v\u1edbi Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-phu-nhan-mua-cillessen-vao-thang-1-172-195029.html\">Man City ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn mua sao Barca v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2674","checkdouble":"195107"},{"date":"07:52 23/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 23/8: Son Heung-min c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn M.U \u2013 Tottenham","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/5/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-238-son-heungmin-co-the-gop-mat-o-dai-chien-mu-tottenham.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tuy\u1ec3n Anh l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng chia s\u1ebb quan \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1ec1 c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea th\u0103ng hoa, Arsenal ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 London \u0111\u1ec1u thay t\u01b0\u1edbng, v\u1edbi Maurizio Sarri k\u1ebf nhi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Antonio Conte \u1edf Chelsea v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t Arsenal chia tay Arsene Wenger sau 22 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3n v\u1ec1 Unai Emery.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, thay t\u01b0\u1edbng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1eadn. T\u00ednh \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn c\u1ee7a c\u00e2u n\u00f3i ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng minh \u1edf Chelsea sau hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean to\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf Premier League 2018/19. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m Arsenal tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u1edbi hai tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n thua v\u00e0 v\u1eabn l\u1eadn \u0111\u1eadn.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ashley Cole nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Arsenal vs Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ashley Cole nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Arsenal vs Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/ashley-cole-danh-gia-trai-nguoc-arsenal-va-chelsea-nam-nay.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ashley Cole nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Arsenal vs Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Sau tr\u1eadn derby cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n qua khi Sarri \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Emery, Ashley Cole \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t, \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u1ea3n r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tuy\u1ec3n Anh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o CLB LA Galaxy c\u1ee7a M\u1ef9 v\u1edbi t\u1ea5m b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n \u0111eo tay:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;Chelsea kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri nh\u01b0ng theo c\u00e1ch t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i \u00e2m th\u1ea7n, \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00fac n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd, c\u00f2n t\u00f4i th\u00ec cho r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. S\u00e1u \u0111i\u1ec3m tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i sau hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi m\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;V\u1edbi Arsenal, h\u1ecd \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi tri\u1ebft l\u00fd b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Emery. H\u00e3y hi\u1ec3u cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n ch\u00fat n\u00e0o khi \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 xem b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng th\u00f4i m\u00e0 c\u0169ng c\u00f2n c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c l\u1ea1 l\u1eabm, ch\u01b0a quen thu\u1ed9c khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n Arsene Wenger \u0111\u1ee9ng b\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng pitch. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00edch h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y ra \u0111i v\u00e0 ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Arsenal ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n West Ham tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Emirates trong khi Chelsea h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn St. James&rsquo; Park l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Newcastle v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-chelsea-vs-arsenal-tien-dao-alvaro-morata-172-194782.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/140159-4.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-chelsea-vs-arsenal-tien-dao-alvaro-morata-172-194782.html\">Chelsea th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb Derby London: Ng\u00e0y Sarri h\u1ed3i sinh Morata</span><br>\r\nC\u00f3 th\u1ec3 anh \u0111\u00e3 xem Diego Costa h\u00e0nh h\u1ea1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Real Madrid c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau C\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ecdc c\u00e1c C\u0110V Chelsea vi\u1ebft g\u00ec v\u1ec1 m\u00ecnh tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-thua-tran-thu-hai-lien-tiep-unai-emery-can-them-bao-nhieu-thoi-gian-172-194779.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/arsenal-thua-tran-thu-hai-lien-tiep-unai-emery-can-them-bao-nhieu-thoi-gian.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-thua-tran-thu-hai-lien-tiep-unai-emery-can-them-bao-nhieu-thoi-gian-172-194779.html\">Arsenal thua tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp: Unai Emery c\u1ea7n th\u00eam bao nhi\u00eau th\u1eddi gian?</span><br>\r\nTh\u00eam nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed5 x\u1ebb sau khi Arsenal \u0111\u1ec3 thua Chelsea nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a Unai Emery v\u1eabn mang \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2673","checkdouble":"195108"},{"date":"08:34 23/08","title":"Ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Mesut Ozil ch\u1ec9 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng k\u1ebb \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/Nguoi-Bayern-Munich-chi-trich-Mesut-Ozil-chia-tay-doi-tuyen-Duc-hinh-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jurgen Klopp l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Mesut Ozil. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c cho r\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng v\u00e0 mang nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ozil h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu b\u00faa r\u00ecu d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMesut Ozil v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c, Ilkay Gundogan \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i l\u1edbn trong d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 5 v\u1eeba qua. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p v\u00e0 ch\u1ee5p h\u00ecnh c\u00f9ng t\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3, Recep Tayyip Erdogan &ndash; nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau m\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay c\u1ea3 khi Ozil v\u00e0 Gundogan c\u00f3 g\u1ed1c g\u00e1c Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m. M\u1ed7i khi kho\u00e1c l\u00ean m\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c sau \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch gay g\u1eaft. S\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Ozil v\u00e0 Gundogan n\u00f3i ri\u00eang v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c n\u00f3i chung cho World Cup 2018 t\u1ea1i Nga \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jurgen Klopp l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Mesut Ozil h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jurgen Klopp l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Mesut Ozil h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/Nguoi-Bayern-Munich-chi-trich-Mesut-Ozil-chia-tay-doi-tuyen-Duc-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Jurgen Klopp l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Mesut Ozil</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ebft b\u00e1t, s\u1edbm b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. C\u00f2n Ozil th\u00ec ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u1ecbu ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch d\u1eef d\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn trong n\u01b0\u1edbc d\u1eabn t\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e3 t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Klopp l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJurgen Klopp l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Mesut Ozil v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 t\u1ea1i Borussia Dortmund l\u00e0 Ilkay Gundogan. HLV c\u1ee7a Liverpool tin r\u1eb1ng ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch d\u00e0nh cho b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3. &ldquo;\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u00ed d\u1ee5 \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 th\u00f4ng tin tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i sai l\u1ea1c v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean, n\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng mang nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ngh\u0129a&rdquo;, Klopp n\u00f3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Trong ch\u00ednh tr\u1ecb, nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u nh\u1ecf nh\u1eb7t lu\u00f4n b\u1ecb th\u1ed5i bay v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u1ee9 l\u1edbn lao b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean. Th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00f4ng minh c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng \u00e9m l\u1ea1i v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i ra nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn. Nh\u1eefng k\u1ebb m\u1ea5t tr\u00ed th\u01b0\u1eddng r\u1ea5t to ti\u1ebfng trong nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c tranh lu\u1eadn nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 Ilkay Gundogan v\u00e0 Emre Can. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 Mesut Ozil, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 h\u1ecd, \u00edt nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 trung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. S\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t (ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c). V\u1eady ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb \u0111\u00e2u?&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Mesut Ozil tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/carragher-chi-ra-2-mat-xich-yeu-nhat-trong-doi-hinh-arsenal-172-195090.html\">Carragher ch\u1ec9 ra 2 m\u1eaft x\u00edch y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ozil-dang-phai-chien-dau-cho-tuong-lai-o-arsenal-172-195031.html\">Ozil \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u1edf Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-thua-dau-emery-van-vui-vi-ozil-biet-nghe-loi-172-194797.html\">Arsenal thua \u0111au, Emery v\u1eabn vui v\u00ec Ozil... bi\u1ebft nghe l\u1eddi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-bao-ve-thoi-luoi-phong-ngu-cua-ozil-172-194723.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00f3i l\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Ozil</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-unai-emery-nhac-mesut-ozil-tich-cuc-tham-gia-phong-ngu-hon-172-194714.html\">HLV Unai Emery nh\u1eafc Mesut Ozil t\u00edch c\u1ef1c tham gia ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u01a1n</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2672","checkdouble":"195109"},{"date":"08:05 23/08","title":"HLV Bahrain t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/hlv-bahrain-tu-tin-truoc-tran-dau-voi-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Bahrain v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay, HLV Samir Chammam tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo.\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Bahrain t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Bahrain t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/23/flf1534947226.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Bahrain t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. \u1ea2nh: Zing.vn</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h30 t\u1ed1i nay, \u0110T Olympic Bahrain s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 ASIAD g\u1eb7p Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV Samir Chammam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u1ea1c quan v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng chia s\u1ebb: &quot;\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y l\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Bahrain. T\u00f4i mong h\u1ecd s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bahrain \u0111\u00e3 thua H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 0-6 trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n \u1edf b\u1ea3ng E Asiad 2018. Tr\u1eadn thua \u0111\u1eadm n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 \u00f4ng&nbsp;Chammam b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean tr\u00ean nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u00f3, Bahrain \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 n\u00e9t qua t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 3-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Malaysia \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 v\u00e9 tham d\u1ef1 v\u00f2ng 1/8.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, \u00f4ng Chammam cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u00f3 b\u1ed1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018, v\u00e0 h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. V\u1eady n\u00ean, y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t th\u1ea5y r\u00f5. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf. H\u1ecd b\u1ecb ng\u1ee3p v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i khi v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn, n\u00ean m\u1edbi d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf. N\u1ebfu c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u00e3 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c h\u01a1n&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo HLV&nbsp;Chammam, Olympic Bahrain \u0111ang g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1edbi kh\u00e2u d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m. H\u1ecd b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Malaysia 3-2 m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Song nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y c\u0169ng hy v\u1ecdng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 s\u1ebd c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf n\u00e0y \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Chammam c\u0169ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp d\u00f9 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-19h30-ngay-238-viet-tiep-ky-tich-168-195103.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-19h30-ngay-238-viet-tiep-ky-tich.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-19h30-ngay-238-viet-tiep-ky-tich-168-195103.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain (19h30 ng\u00e0y 23/8): Vi\u1ebft ti\u1ebfp k\u1ef3 t\u00edch</span><br>\r\n19h30 t\u1ed1i nay, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra. V\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-malaysia-hy-vong-olympic-viet-nam-se-tien-xa-tai-asiad-2018-168-195102.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/11/22/bao-nuoc-ngoai-nhan-dinh-gi-ve-tran-viet-nam-vs-malaysia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-malaysia-hy-vong-olympic-viet-nam-se-tien-xa-tai-asiad-2018-168-195102.html\">HLV Malaysia hy v\u1ecdng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn xa t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Olympic Malaysia Ong Kim Swee \u0111\u00e3 hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn xa t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-don-hung-tin-ve-nhan-su-truoc-tran-gap-bahrain-168-195101.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/olympic-viet-nam-don-hung-tin-ve-nhan-su-truoc-tran-gap-bahrain.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-don-hung-tin-ve-nhan-su-truoc-tran-gap-bahrain-168-195101.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00f3n hung tin v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Bahrain</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Bahrain t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng knock-out v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t tin kh\u00f4ng vui v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%;&#10;font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2671","checkdouble":"195110"},{"date":"08:35 23/08","title":"Ashley Cole \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea n\u0103m nay","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/ashley-cole-danh-gia-trai-nguoc-arsenal-va-chelsea-nam-nay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tuy\u1ec3n Anh l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng chia s\u1ebb quan \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1ec1 c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea th\u0103ng hoa, Arsenal ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 London \u0111\u1ec1u thay t\u01b0\u1edbng, v\u1edbi Maurizio Sarri k\u1ebf nhi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Antonio Conte \u1edf Chelsea v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t Arsenal chia tay Arsene Wenger sau 22 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3n v\u1ec1 Unai Emery.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, thay t\u01b0\u1edbng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1eadn. T\u00ednh \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn c\u1ee7a c\u00e2u n\u00f3i ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng minh \u1edf Chelsea sau hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean to\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf Premier League 2018/19. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m Arsenal tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u1edbi hai tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n thua v\u00e0 v\u1eabn l\u1eadn \u0111\u1eadn.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ashley Cole nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Arsenal vs Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ashley Cole nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Arsenal vs Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/ashley-cole-danh-gia-trai-nguoc-arsenal-va-chelsea-nam-nay.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ashley Cole nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Arsenal vs Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Sau tr\u1eadn derby cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n qua khi Sarri \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Emery, Ashley Cole \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t, \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u1ea3n r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tuy\u1ec3n Anh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o CLB LA Galaxy c\u1ee7a M\u1ef9 v\u1edbi t\u1ea5m b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n \u0111eo tay:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;Chelsea kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri nh\u01b0ng theo c\u00e1ch t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i \u00e2m th\u1ea7n, \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00fac n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd, c\u00f2n t\u00f4i th\u00ec cho r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. S\u00e1u \u0111i\u1ec3m tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i sau hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi m\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;V\u1edbi Arsenal, h\u1ecd \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi tri\u1ebft l\u00fd b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Emery. H\u00e3y hi\u1ec3u cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n ch\u00fat n\u00e0o khi \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 xem b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng th\u00f4i m\u00e0 c\u0169ng c\u00f2n c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c l\u1ea1 l\u1eabm, ch\u01b0a quen thu\u1ed9c khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n Arsene Wenger \u0111\u1ee9ng b\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng pitch. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00edch h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y ra \u0111i v\u00e0 ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Arsenal ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n West Ham tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Emirates trong khi Chelsea h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn St. James&rsquo; Park l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Newcastle v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-chelsea-vs-arsenal-tien-dao-alvaro-morata-172-194782.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/140159-4.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-chelsea-vs-arsenal-tien-dao-alvaro-morata-172-194782.html\">Chelsea th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb Derby London: Ng\u00e0y Sarri h\u1ed3i sinh Morata</span><br>\r\nC\u00f3 th\u1ec3 anh \u0111\u00e3 xem Diego Costa h\u00e0nh h\u1ea1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Real Madrid c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau C\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ecdc c\u00e1c C\u0110V Chelsea vi\u1ebft g\u00ec v\u1ec1 m\u00ecnh tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-thua-tran-thu-hai-lien-tiep-unai-emery-can-them-bao-nhieu-thoi-gian-172-194779.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/arsenal-thua-tran-thu-hai-lien-tiep-unai-emery-can-them-bao-nhieu-thoi-gian.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-thua-tran-thu-hai-lien-tiep-unai-emery-can-them-bao-nhieu-thoi-gian-172-194779.html\">Arsenal thua tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp: Unai Emery c\u1ea7n th\u00eam bao nhi\u00eau th\u1eddi gian?</span><br>\r\nTh\u00eam nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed5 x\u1ebb sau khi Arsenal \u0111\u1ec3 thua Chelsea nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a Unai Emery v\u1eabn mang \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2670","checkdouble":"195111"},{"date":"08:13 23/08","title":"\u201cOlympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem nh\u1eb9 Bahrain\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/olympic-viet-nam-khong-duoc-xem-nhe-bahrain.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1ee7 quan tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem nh\u1eb9 Bahrain</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 nh\u1edd s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong khi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 t\u1eadp h\u1ee3p nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a l\u1ee9a U21.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem nh\u1eb9 Bahrain h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem nh\u1eb9 Bahrain h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/29/Olympic-Viet-Nam-khong-duoc-xem-nhe-Bahrain-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh hy v\u1ecdng&nbsp;Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1ee7 quan tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bahrain</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, c\u1ef1u HLV SLNA Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh \u0111\u00e3 t\u00e2m s\u1ef1 v\u1edbi b\u00e1o Th\u1ec3 thao V\u0103n h\u00f3a: &ldquo;Sau khi gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng D v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch 3 tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n th\u1eafng, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i tinh th\u1ea7n h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 tin.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng cho tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u v\u00f2ng 1/8. Khi V\u0110V \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n t\u1ed1t, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1edf phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 t\u1edbi 3 ng\u00e0y n\u00ean c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngu\u1ed3n th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c sung m\u00e3n tr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Bahrain&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh hy v\u1ecdng h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd gi\u1eef v\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb T\u00e2y \u00c1 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Tr\u1ea3i qua 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ec3 thua b\u00e0n n\u00e0o. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng khen ng\u1ee3i.&nbsp;Hy v\u1ecdng, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn trong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Bahrain.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bahrain \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 qua t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. H\u1ecd thua H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 0-6, tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 ho\u00e0 Kyrgyzstan 2-2, tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng h\u1ecd th\u1eafng Malaysia 3-2. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ch\u1ee7 quan tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Bahrain (3 th\u1eafng, 1 thua). G\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ee7a HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n t\u1eebng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 U19 Bahrain 1-0, qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 VCK U20 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi 2017.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-19h30-ngay-238-viet-tiep-ky-tich-168-195103.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-19h30-ngay-238-viet-tiep-ky-tich.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-19h30-ngay-238-viet-tiep-ky-tich-168-195103.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain (19h30 ng\u00e0y 23/8): Vi\u1ebft ti\u1ebfp k\u1ef3 t\u00edch</span><br>\r\n19h30 t\u1ed1i nay, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra. V\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-bahrain-tu-tin-truoc-tran-dau-voi-olympic-viet-nam-168-195110.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/hlv-bahrain-tu-tin-truoc-tran-dau-voi-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-bahrain-tu-tin-truoc-tran-dau-voi-olympic-viet-nam-168-195110.html\">HLV Bahrain t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Bahrain v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay, HLV Samir Chammam tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-don-hung-tin-ve-nhan-su-truoc-tran-gap-bahrain-168-195101.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/olympic-viet-nam-don-hung-tin-ve-nhan-su-truoc-tran-gap-bahrain.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-don-hung-tin-ve-nhan-su-truoc-tran-gap-bahrain-168-195101.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00f3n hung tin v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Bahrain</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Bahrain t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng knock-out v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t tin kh\u00f4ng vui v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2669","checkdouble":"195112"},{"date":"08:38 23/08","title":"Ronaldo v\u00e0 Zidane s\u1eafp t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p \u1edf Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/5/29/Zidane Ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Zinedine Zidane d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Juventus l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111\u00e3 ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p thay Massimiliano Allegri.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Juventus \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n thay th\u1ebf Allegri</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMassimiliano Allegri \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Juventus trong 4 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0o \u00f4ng c\u0169ng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Serie A. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Zinedine Zidane d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Juventus thay Allegri \u1edf H\u00e8 2019 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Zinedine Zidane d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Juventus thay Allegri \u1edf H\u00e8 2019 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/21/Zinedine-Zidane-dan-dat-Juventus-thay-Allegri-o-He-2019-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Juventus c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi HLV Allegri v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 l\u00e0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 5 c\u1ee7a Allegri \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin, n\u1ebfu \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia kh\u00f4ng gi\u00fap Juventus v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Juventus s\u1ebd t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t HLV m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ngay t\u1eeb th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean thay th\u1ebf Allegri \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus nh\u1eafm Zidane thay Allegri</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Zinedine Zidane d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Juventus l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111\u00e3 ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p thay Massimiliano Allegri.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo v\u00e0 Zidane s\u1eafp t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p \u1edf Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Ronaldo v\u00e0 Zidane s\u1eafp t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p \u1edf Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/Ronaldo-va-Zidane-sap-tai-hop-o-Juventus-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Juventus nh\u1eafm Zidane thay Allegri</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Zidane \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho Juventus t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1996 \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2001, gi\u1eefa nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 \u201cB\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0\u201d v\u1eabn c\u00f3 quan h\u1ec7 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u00f4ng quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBL\u0110 Juventus \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, \u00f4ng tin Zidane s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Ronaldo, h\u1ecd tin r\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a CR7 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Zidane \u0111\u1ebfn Italia cao h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Ronaldo v\u00e0 Zidane \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u1edf Real Madrid, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng nhau gi\u00e0nh 3 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp. Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn CR7 mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y c\u0169 \u1edf Juventus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 Juventus c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/zidane-duoc-ung-ho-thay-the-mourinho-o-man-utd-172-195020.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU c\u0169ng nh\u1eafm Zidane thay Mourinho</span>, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho c\u1ef1u HLV Real m\u1ed9t m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t cao, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u00f4ng mua s\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2668","checkdouble":"195114"},{"date":"08:53 23/08","title":"HLV Sarri \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Loftus-Cheek","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/hlv-sarri-dau-dau-ve-tuong-lai-loftuscheek.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ruben Loftus-Cheek r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n, HLV Sarri \u0111ang g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u1edf l\u1ea1i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Loftus-Cheek \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Loftus-Cheek ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Crystal Palace theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. V\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp v\u00e0o \u0110T Anh tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018, \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Sarri kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Ruben Loftus-Cheek r\u1eddi Chelsea  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Sarri kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Ruben Loftus-Cheek r\u1eddi Chelsea  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/23/hlv-sarri-dau-dau-ve-tuong-lai-loftuscheek.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Loftus-Cheek mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tu\u1ed5i 22, Loftus-Cheek \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a The Blues \u0111ang c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1i t\u00ean ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1996 gi\u1ea3m \u0111i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRuben Loftus-Cheek r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n, hi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf T\u00e2y Ban Nha, \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh. Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a, h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Loftus-Cheek ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-chot-tuong-lai-loftuscheek-172-194984.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 Loftus-Cheek ra \u0111i</span>, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, qua \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn. Tuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Loftus-Cheek ch\u1ec9 \u1edf l\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo t\u1edd Mirror, Ruben Loftus-Cheek \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1eb7p HLV Sarri \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. Ng\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ed5 l\u1ed9 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, anh mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb h\u00e0ng tu\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Sarri kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Ruben Loftus-Cheek r\u1eddi Chelsea  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Sarri kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Ruben Loftus-Cheek r\u1eddi Chelsea  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/23/Loftus-Cheek.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Loftus-Cheek \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn HLV Sarri \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 b\u00e0i to\u00e1n kh\u00f3 v\u1edbi HLV Sarri, b\u1edfi v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111ang c\u00f3 trong tay r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u00f4ng n\u00e0y trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, c\u1ef1u HLV Napoli mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef Ruben Loftus-Cheek \u1edf l\u1ea1i, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho anh \u1edf nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 FA Cup hay C\u00fap li\u00ean \u0110o\u00e0n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1eeb nay \u0111\u1ebfn khi phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n kho\u1ea3ng m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn HLV Sarri s\u1ebd \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDaily Mail th\u00ec kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i do kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Arsenal, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1eed s\u1ee9c trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2667","checkdouble":"195115"},{"date":"08:49 23/08","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP ASIAD 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 23/8","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/23/asiad-2018-ngay-hom-nay-238.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ASIAD 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 23/8: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn, th\u00f4ng tin, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c V\u0110V thu\u1ed9c \u0111o\u00e0n th\u1ec3 thao Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 23/8.</h2>(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)\r\n<h2>LINK XEM TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP ASIAD 2018 C\u00d3 B\u1ea2N QUY\u1ec0N</h2>\r\nLINK 1:&nbsp;<span href=\"https://fptplay.vn/livetv/vtc3-hd\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://fptplay.vn/livetv/vtc3-hd</span><br>\r\n<br>\r\nLINK 2: <span href=\"https://vtc.gov.vn/kenh/vtc3\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://vtc.gov.vn/kenh/vtc3</span><br>\r\n<br>\r\nLINK 3:&nbsp;<span href=\"https://vtc.gov.vn/kenh/vtc3\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://vovtv.vov.vn</span><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/bang-tong-sap-huy-chuong-asiad-2018-472-194760.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/bang-tong-sap-huy-chuong-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/asiad-2018/bang-tong-sap-huy-chuong-asiad-2018-472-194760.html\">B\u1ea2NG T\u1ed4NG S\u1eaeP HUY CH\u01af\u01a0NG ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\n<span>Chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u1ebd c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c B\u1ea3ng t\u1ed5ng s\u1eafp huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng ASIAD 2018, B\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng Asiad 2018 c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n Th\u1ec3 Thao Vi\u1ec7t Nam di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>TH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH C\u1ee6A TTVN T\u1ea0I ASIAD 2018</h2>\r\n3 HCB<br>\r\n- Th\u1ea1ch Kim Tu\u1ea5n (c\u1eed t\u1ea1, 56kg nam)<br>\r\n- Ph\u1ea1m Qu\u1ed1c Kh\u00e1nh (wushu)<br>\r\n- Tr\u1ecbnh V\u0103n Vinh (c\u1eed t\u1ea1, 62kg nam)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n7 HC\u0110<br>\r\n- Taekwondo (n\u1ed9i dung quy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i nam)<br>\r\n- B\u1eafn s\u00fang (10m s\u00fang ng\u1eafn h\u01a1i h\u1ed7n h\u1ee3p nam n\u1eef).<br>\r\n- Nguy\u1ec5n Huy Ho\u00e0ng (b\u01a1i 800m t\u1ef1 do nam)<br>\r\n- D\u01b0\u01a1ng Th\u00fay Vi (wushu)<br>\r\n- Ho\u00e0ng Th\u1ecb Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng Giang (tr\u01b0\u1eddng quy\u1ec1n n\u1eef, wushu)<br>\r\n- C\u1ea7u m\u00e2y (Regu \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i n\u1eef)<br>\r\n- Nghi\u00eam V\u0103n \u00dd (Wushu T\u00e1n th\u1ee7 h\u1ea1ng c\u00e2n d\u01b0\u1edbi 60kg nam)<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong ng\u00e0y 23/8, s\u1ebd c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 42 b\u1ed9 huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao, ni\u1ec1m hi v\u1ecdng V\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a TTVN \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o v\u00f5 s\u0129 B\u00f9i Tr\u01b0\u1eddng Giang \u1edf h\u1ea1ng c\u00e2n d\u01b0\u1edbi 56kg (wushu, \u0111\u1ed1i kh\u00e1ng). Tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft gi\u1eefa V\u00f5 s\u0129 Tr\u01b0\u1eddng Giang v\u00e0 V\u0110V c\u1ee7a Trung Qu\u1ed1c Shen Goshun di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 10h20 s\u00e1ng nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00f4m nay c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00f4n pencak silat. Ba V\u0110V Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f9ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/16 g\u1ed3m: Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u00ecnh Tu\u1ea5n \u1edf h\u1ea1ng c\u1eadn 50 - 55 kg, Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e1i Linh \u1edf h\u1ea1ng c\u00e2n 60 - 65 kg, v\u00e0 Ho\u00e0ng Th\u1ecb Loan \u1edf h\u1ea1ng c\u00e2n 60 - 65 kg.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/23/1_2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede c\u00e1c n\u1ed9i dung \u0111\u1ed1i kh\u00e1ng, hy v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a taekwondo Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ed5 d\u1ed3n v\u00e0o Tr\u01b0\u01a1ng Th\u1ecb Kim Tuy\u1ec1n. Chi\u1ebfc HCB h\u1ea1ng c\u00e2n d\u01b0\u1edbi 46 kg c\u1ee7a Kim Tuy\u1ec1n t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi 2017 h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 6 \u1edf H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh t\u00edch m\u1edbi t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a taekwondo Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f4 g\u00e1i sinh n\u0103m 1997 t\u1eebng gi\u00e0nh HCV h\u1ea1ng 46kg n\u1eef t\u1ea1i SEA Games 28 v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111o\u1ea1t ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch t\u1ea1i Gi\u1ea3i Taekwondo qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2015. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean t\u1ea1i SEA Games 2017, Kim Tuy\u1ec1n ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HCB sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f5 s\u1ef9 Th\u00e1i Lan \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m qu\u00fd b\u00e1u \u0111\u1ec3 Tuy\u1ec1n r\u00fat ra b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc cho cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u00f2n kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t h\u01a1n t\u1ea1i ASIAD.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD, Kim Tuy\u1ec1n ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o khi v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Taekwondo \u0111\u1ed1i kh\u00e1ng ch\u00e2u \u00c1 h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 5. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed1i kh\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a taekwondo Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf gi\u1ea3i ch\u00e2u \u00c1 k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a Nguy\u1ec5n Tr\u1ecdng C\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ea1ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 87kg nam n\u0103m 2012.\r\n<h2>L\u1ecaCH THI \u0110\u1ea4U ASIAD 2018 NG\u00c0Y H\u00d4M NAY 23/8 C\u1ee6A \u0110O\u00c0N TTVN</h2>\r\n<table style=\"border-collapse:collapse;border:3px double #000000;\" width=\"100%\" border=\"1\" align=\"center\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td height=\"30\" bgcolor=\"#008000\" align=\"center\">\r\n            <p style=\"margin: 1px\"><b><font size=\"2\" face=\"Arial\" color=\"#FFFFFF\"> \t\tTh\u1eddi gian</font></b></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td height=\"30\" bgcolor=\"#008000\" align=\"center\">\r\n            <p style=\"margin: 1px\"><b><font size=\"2\" face=\"Arial\" color=\"#FFFFFF\"> \t\tN\u1ed9i dung</font></b></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td height=\"30\" bgcolor=\"#008000\" align=\"center\">\r\n            <p style=\"margin: 1px\"><b><font size=\"2\" face=\"Arial\" color=\"#FFFFFF\"> \t\tV\u00f2ng</font></b></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td height=\"30\" bgcolor=\"#008000\" align=\"center\">\r\n            <p style=\"margin: 1px\"><b><font size=\"2\" face=\"Arial\" color=\"#FFFFFF\"> \t\tV\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean</font></b></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td colspan=\"4\" style=\"width: 768.0pt; height: 23.55pt; border-left: 1.0pt solid black; border-right: 1.0pt solid black; border-top: medium none; border-bottom: 1px solid black; padding: 0in; background: #E1EEDA\" width=\"1024\" valign=\"top\">\r\n            <p class=\"TableParagraph\" style=\"margin-left: 1px; margin-right: 1px; margin-