0y 22/8.</h2><h2>Marseille kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu Yaya Toure</h2>\r\n<div>Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Marseille l\u00e0 Jacques-Henri Eyraud cho bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Velodrome kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Yaya Toure. C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man City hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ef1 do sau khi chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester h\u00e8 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Marseille kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Toure \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf cho Zambo-Anguissa m\u1edbi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Fulham.</div>\r\n<h2>Draxler c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn La Liga</h2>\r\n<div>Theo ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Sevilla \u0111ang mong mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Draxler c\u1ee7a PSG. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed l\u00fac n\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Wissam Ben Yedder s\u1ebd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Marseille ngay sau \u0111\u00f3.</div>\r\n<h2>Martial quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i MU</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 228 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 228 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/Duoc-BLD-ung-ho-Martial-quyet-tam-chung-to-minh-o-MU-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 22/8: Martial quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>T\u1edd The Sun \u0111\u01b0a tin ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Anthony Martial \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i Man United ngay d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Mourinho. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 t\u1ea1i Nga v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf MU. Anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y.</div>\r\n<h2>Kante s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div>T\u1edd Le10Sport kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 N&rsquo;golo Kante \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp theo. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i theo \u0111u\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 Real Madrid hay Paris Saint-Germain. Nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Kante \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Chelsea d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Maurizio Sarri.</div>\r\n<h2>Man City nh\u1eafm th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n kh\u1ee7ng thay th\u1ebf Bravo</h2>\r\n<div>K\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Premier League nh\u01b0ng Man City \u0111ang nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Keylor Navas t\u1eeb Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Claudio Bravo. Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Chile nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 c\u1ea3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u00f3t ch\u00e2n. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, Man xanh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 Ederson. V\u1edbi m\u1ed9t HLV th\u00edch xoay tua nh\u01b0 Pep Guardiola, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn. V\u00e0 v\u00ec v\u1eady, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang mong mu\u1ed1n Man City c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Navas c\u00e0ng s\u1edbm c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t.</div>\r\n<div>Bongda24h.vn (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2665","checkdouble":"195094"},{"date":"19:41 22/08","title":"Ronaldo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/22/ronaldo-tiet-lo-ly-do-dau-quan-cho-juventus.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Cristiano Ronaldo th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn s\u1ef1 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 m\u00e0 c\u00e1c C\u0110V Juventus d\u00e0nh cho anh sau pha \u201cng\u1ea3 b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e8n\u201d l\u1ecbch s\u1eed h\u1ed3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh \u0111\u01b0a anh t\u1edbi th\u00e0nh Turin.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eddi cho Real Madrid v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Juventus \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i Champions League n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i t\u1ea1i Turin. Pha b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c C\u0110V c\u1ee7a Juventus c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady c\u1ed5 v\u0169 anh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u00e1c Juventini c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u1edd r\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd khi \u1ea5y l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh \u0111\u01b0a Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cristiano Ronaldo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Cristiano Ronaldo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/22/ronaldo-tiet-lo-ly-do-dau-quan-cho-juventus.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ef1 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c C\u0110V Juve l\u00e0 l\u00fd do anh \u0111\u1ebfn Turin</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cNh\u1eefng chi ti\u1ebft nh\u1ecf l\u1ea1i th\u01b0\u1eddng mang \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1edbn. Nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00f4i nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a Juventus khi \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y. D\u0129 nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 chi ti\u1ebft \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh 100% th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y nh\u01b0ng n\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i suy ngh\u0129\u201d.</em><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 33 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a anh khi \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng t\u1ea1o ra ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c C\u0110V Real m\u00e0 anh ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng th\u1ea5y tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 bao gi\u1edd.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cB\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i cho \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Khi m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u khen ng\u1ee3i b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng, c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c qu\u00e1 s\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cN\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u1edfi v\u00ec t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea5y \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc kh\u00f3 tin trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i\u201d.</em><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft Juventus trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Chievo tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Tuy v\u1eady, si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng n\u00e0o trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Juventus:<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/hang-loat-doi-bong-lon-nhan-don-dau-vu-pjanic-176-195028.html\">H\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f2n \u0111au v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-khong-the-giup-juventus-tiep-tuc-thong-tri-nuoc-y-176-195019.html\">Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Juventus ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)\u00a0</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2664","checkdouble":"195095"},{"date":"21:25 22/08","title":"\"Justin Kluivert \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00fang khi t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i MU\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/30/justin-kluivert-da-dung-khi-tu-choi-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n \u0110T Olympic Bahrain t\u1ecf ra \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t c\u00f3 trong tay HLV Park Hang Seo.\r\n\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n Bahrain ch\u1ec9 ra 3 ng\u00f4i sao nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 23/8, \u0110T Olympic Bahrain s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i &lsquo;m\u1ed9t m\u1ea5t, m\u1ed9t c\u00f2n&rsquo; v\u1edbi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 tham d\u1ef1 v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n \u0110T Olympic Bahrain Ahmed Bin Isa Al Khalifa \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t. D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra am hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Van Quyet\" title=\"V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/truong-doan-bahrain-chi-ra-3-ngoi-sao-nguy-hiem-nhat-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 3 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n \u0110T Olympic Bahrain \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng Ahmed n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Zing.vn: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i m\u1edbi xem m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t kinh nghi\u1ec7m. \u0110i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 10 (V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft) ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 s\u1ed1 18 (H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng) v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 19 (Quang H\u1ea3i).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f4i h\u01a1i ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean v\u00ec sao h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng thua g\u00ec c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n hay H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. S\u1ed1 19 c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n h\u01a1n n\u1ebfu ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a qu\u00ean tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a Bahrain tr\u01b0\u1edbc U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, khi h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 U20 World Cup. &ldquo;&ldquo;U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu. H\u1ecd ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng nhanh r\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 thua v\u00ec b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 ng\u00e0y mai s\u1ebd ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i. Olympic Bahrain s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft ASIAD&rdquo;, v\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n&nbsp;29 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y chia s\u1ebb.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1ecb n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Bahrain s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Malaysia \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n Ahmed Bin Isa kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: &ldquo;\u0110\u00e3 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out, b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 t\u1eebng th\u1eafng Olympic Malaysia&rdquo;.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-19h30-ngay-238-viet-tiep-ky-tich-168-195103.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-19h30-ngay-238-viet-tiep-ky-tich.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-19h30-ngay-238-viet-tiep-ky-tich-168-195103.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain (19h30 ng\u00e0y 23/8): Vi\u1ebft ti\u1ebfp k\u1ef3 t\u00edch</span><br />\r\n19h30 t\u1ed1i nay, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra. V\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-malaysia-hy-vong-olympic-viet-nam-se-tien-xa-tai-asiad-2018-168-195102.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/11/22/bao-nuoc-ngoai-nhan-dinh-gi-ve-tran-viet-nam-vs-malaysia.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-malaysia-hy-vong-olympic-viet-nam-se-tien-xa-tai-asiad-2018-168-195102.html\">HLV Malaysia hy v\u1ecdng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn xa t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</span><br />\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Olympic Malaysia Ong Kim Swee \u0111\u00e3 hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn xa t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-don-hung-tin-ve-nhan-su-truoc-tran-gap-bahrain-168-195101.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/olympic-viet-nam-don-hung-tin-ve-nhan-su-truoc-tran-gap-bahrain.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-don-hung-tin-ve-nhan-su-truoc-tran-gap-bahrain-168-195101.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00f3n hung tin v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Bahrain</span><br />\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Bahrain t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng knock-out v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t tin kh\u00f4ng vui v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2663","checkdouble":"195096"},{"date":"21:48 22/08","title":"Pep Guardiola tri \u00e2n Kompany nh\u00e2n d\u1ecbp \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/14/pep-guardiola-khen-ngoi-kompany-het-loi.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Pep Guardiola cho r\u1eb1ng Vincent Kompany l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong ng\u00e0y ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m 10 n\u0103m \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u00e2n t\u1edbi Etihad.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kompany gia nh\u1eadp Man City t\u1eeb Hamburg v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 22/8/2008 v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng 7.65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, Kompany \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester gi\u00e0nh 3 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League, 3 League Cup, 1 FA Cup v\u00e0 2 Community Shield.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i sao 32 tu\u1ed5i g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Pep Guardiola v\u00ec nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Anh ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 28 l\u1ea7n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng trong 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pep Guardiola tri \u00e2n Kompany nh\u00e2n d\u1ecbp \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Pep Guardiola tri \u00e2n Kompany nh\u00e2n d\u1ecbp \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/14/pep-guardiola-khen-ngoi-kompany-het-loi.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Pep Guardiola tri \u00e2n Kompany</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Guardiola v\u1eabn l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tri \u00e2n nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh t\u1ef1u c\u1ee7a Kompany trong v\u00f2ng 1 th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 qua v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cKhi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi 10 n\u0103m th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u1edfi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t. V\u1eady n\u00ean t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi Kompany trong kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00e3 qua. B\u00e2y gi\u1edd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc sang n\u0103m th\u1ee9 3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng nhau. C\u1ea3m \u01a1n c\u1eadu r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, Vincent\u201d.</em><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Kompany c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ch\u00fac m\u1eebng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 trong d\u1ecbp k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb n\u00e0y. Bravo cho bi\u1ebft: <em>\u201cR\u1ea5t \u00edt c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 vinh d\u1ef1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p nh\u01b0 Kompany v\u1edbi Man City\u201d.</em><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Benjamin Mendy c\u0169ng vui m\u1eebng chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean Twitter: <em>\u201cAnh \u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c sinh ra \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1eafn li\u1ec1n v\u1edbi CLB n\u00e0y. Anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng t\u1ed1t, m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man City:<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-muon-mua-keylor-navas-172-195072.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng, Man City g\u00f5 c\u1eeda Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-tinh-goi-lai-aro-muric-172-195048.html\">Kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n, Man City gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft ra sao?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2662","checkdouble":"195097"},{"date":"22:24 22/08","title":"\"Modric ho\u1eb7c Kante x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng 2018\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/modric-hoac-kante-xung-dang-gianh-qua-bong-vang-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Jermain Jenas cho r\u1eb1ng danh hi\u1ec7u Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t thi\u1ebfu c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi \u00edt b\u00e0n nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0 Modric hay Kante.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 Lionel Messi \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb danh hi\u1ec7u C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. Kaka l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1eebng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c danh hi\u1ec7u Ballon d\u2019Or ngo\u00e0i Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1edd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a CLB. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Jenas tin r\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u \u1edf World Cup nh\u01b0ng ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n c\u0169ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 tr\u1ecdng v\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Modric ho\u1eb7c Kante x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Modric ho\u1eb7c Kante x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/modric-hoac-kante-xung-dang-gianh-qua-bong-vang-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jenas cho r\u1eb1ng Modric x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf m\u1ecdi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh cho danh hi\u1ec7u Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c ch\u00fang ta \u0111ang \u1edf trong m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean thi\u1ebfu \u0111i s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cNh\u1eefng g\u00ec Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n r\u1eb1ng ai trong hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng. Khi b\u1ea1n th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u01b0 Iniesta hay Xavi ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd gi\u00e0nh Ballon d\u2019Or th\u00ec b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn r\u1eb1ng ch\u1eb3ng ai gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00f3 ngo\u00e0i Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi.<br>\r\n<br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cC\u1ea3 hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ngo\u00e0i h\u00e0nh tinh. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 Modric m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, Ribery c\u1ee7a Bayern\u00a0 v\u00e0i n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, b\u1ea1n th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng n\u00e0y nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e9t \u0111\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n<br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cGi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y Kante c\u0169ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u00e0o h\u00e0ng ng\u0169 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u00f9 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi nh\u1eadn nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ghi nh\u1eadn t\u1eeb gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng Ballon d\u2019Or. K\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 sau khi gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khen nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t c\u0169ng l\u00e0 Pogba v\u00ec s\u1ef1 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u kh\u00e1c:<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-tiet-lo-ly-do-dau-quan-cho-juventus-176-195095.html\">Ronaldo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-228-martial-ra-quyet-dinh-ve-tuong-lai-o-mu-184-195094.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 22/8: Martial ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u1edf MU</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2661","checkdouble":"195098"}]}